To filter the HIERARCHY PARENT ALL data for relevant RMBS, apply the following filters within Spotfire:

    PILLAR_3_CLASSIFICATION: Foreign RMBS, US RMBS
    GT_CLASSIFICATION: Aussie RMBS, Dutch_FRMBS, US Alta, US Prime

Select the PARENT_CUSIP and BIII_NPR_KG_FINAL columns.

Ensure the data is for the same reporting period.

Copy and paste the filtered data into the RMBS_kg tab of the SSFA File. Manually drag down column G to assign classifications to all securities."
